request.description:
This endpoint allows users to sign up for a new account.

#### Request Body

- `userName` (text, required): The username of the user.

- `gender` (text): The gender of the user.

- `phone` (text, required): The phone number of the user.

- `address` (text): The address of the user.

- `email` (text, required): The email address of the user.

- `password` (text, required): The password for the account.

- `confirmPassword` (text, required): The confirmation of the password.

- `DOB` (text): The date of birth of the user.


Example:

``` json
{
    "userName": "abdullah",
    "gender": "male",
    "phone": "662665564645",
    "address": "cairo",
    "email": "abdo@gmail.com",
    "password": "5asd4fadf",
    "confirmPassword": "5asd4fadf",
    "DOB": "3-27"
}

 ```

#### Response

- Status: 200

- Content-Type: application/json


``` json
{
    "message": "Done",
    "data": {
        "note": "Please confirm your email"
    }
}

 ```

### If the Email already exist

- Status: 409

- Content-Type: application/json

- The response will include a JSON object with a "message" field


``` json
{
 "message": "Email already exist",
}

 ```

### If the required wasn't sent

- No specific request body parameters were provided.


### Response

- Status: 400

- Content-Type: application/json

- The response will include a JSON object with a "message" field and a "validationError" array. The "validationError" array contains objects with "message", "path", "type", and "context" fields.


#### Example

``` json
{
    "message": "validation result",
    "validationError": [
        {
            "message": "\"userName\" is required",
            "path": [
                "userName"
            ],
            "type": "any.required",
            "context": {
                "label": "userName",
                "key": "userName"
            }
        },
        {
            "message": "\"email\" is required",
            "path": [
                "email"
            ],
            "type": "any.required",
            "context": {
                "label": "email",
                "key": "email"
            }
        },
        {
            "message": "\"password\" is required",
            "path": [
                "password"
            ],
            "type": "any.required",
            "context": {
                "label": "password",
                "key": "password"
            }
        },
        {
            "message": "\"confirmPassword\" is required",
            "path": [
                "confirmPassword"
            ],
            "type": "any.required",
            "context": {
                "label": "confirmPassword",
                "key": "confirmPassword"
            }
        },
        {
            "message": "\"phone\" is required",
            "path": [
                "phone"
            ],
            "type": "any.required",
            "context": {
                "label": "phone",
                "key": "phone"
            }
        }
    ]
}

 ```

